`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffNomadNet`!`Ffff     Off-grid pages and communication
`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffMQTT`!`Ffff         Observer bridge to the internet
`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffCoreScope`!`Ffff    Packet analysis and visualization

